Interface Activatable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MenuHeader, MenuPageButton, NavbarButton, TypedPageButton

    public interface Activatable
    An interface that allows the implementations to decide whether they are the active item in a collection of items (like buttons, links, pills, ...)
